<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC4">
<l>naṉmaiyāl mikka nāṉmaṟaiyāḷarkaḷ</l>
<l>puṉmai ākka karutuvar ātaliṉ</l>
<l>aṉṉaiyāy attaṉāy eṉṉai āṇṭiṭum</l>
<l>taṉmaiyāṉ caṭakōpaṉ eṉ nampiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Because the scholars of the four Vedas,</l>
<l>great with blessings, consider [me] to be vile,</l>
<l>Caṭakōpaṉ, a man of greatness, who rules me completely</l>
<l>as Mother and Father, is my Lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
